name: Harry Benson
description: I am a cool-going man, I am honest and big heart. I have a great sense of humor and can dish it out to make a sad day enjoyable. I laugh often and am very optimistic. I think my smile is contagious : I basically would just like to meet a good hearted woman with strong morals, values and character. I enjoy fishing, I love comedy, especially live stand up.. laughing is the best feeling.
